{"word":"G3357 - μετρίως - metríōs - met-ree'-oce - A little","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετρίως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">metríōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">met-ree'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">A little</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குறைவாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. in due measure"},{"paragraph":"2. moderately"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3358 - μέτρον - métron - met'-ron/3358\">G3358</a>; <i>moderately</i>, that is, <i>slightly:</i> - a little.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G280/280\">G280</a>, <a href=\"#/G3354/3354\">G3354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3357/3357\">G3357</a>, <a href=\"#/G3358/3358\">G3358</a>"}]}